Invocation Name: milky mocha
des: Do you want to test your boyfriend, girlfriend, husband or wife? In this party game for friends or couples, players pair up, and Alexa quizzes each player on how well they know their partner. The partner judges the responses. This brand new skill is the perfect newlywed game before bed and ingenious couples quiz for new lovers – discover how well they know you AND you know them. Plus of course, part of the magic of a relationship game is learning more about yourself!
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
